events_forwarder_unhealthy.description:
CoPilot is queueing events but cannot deliver them to Core. This usually indicates that Core is offline, the token/host is wrong, or networking is blocked.

Current queue depth: {queue_len}
Error streak: {error_streak}
Dropped total: {dropped_total}

Suggested checks: verify Core is online, confirm host/port/token in the integration config, and check logs for connectivity errors.
